==Finnish==
===Noun===

''(obscene)'' kyrpä (plural ''kyrpiä, kyrvät)''

# Male genitalia: cock, dick, prick, schlong.
# Annoying person: asshole, prick.

Finnish synonyms: [[kulli]], [[kikkeli]], [[muna]], [[mulkku]]

===Usage notes===

While the respective female word, ''[[vittu]]'', isn't normally used directly to call someone names, ''kyrpä'' often is. ''Saatanan kyrpä!'' Fucking asshole! (literally "devil's prick")

Sometimes the definite plural form ''kyrvät'' is used for the entire set of male genitalia.

The indefinite plural form ''kyrpiä'' is easily confused to be the basic form of the verb ''[[kyrpii]]''. It is, however, rarely used in this sense. See [[vituttaa]] for closer details.

